text: "Dansez" is a single by Jessy Matador, from his second album Electro Soukouss. The song features vocals from Daddy Killa. It was released on 24 January 2011 in France and managed to peak to number 86 in the French Singles Chart. As of May, 2011, it has had over 300,000 hits on YouTube. ==Track listing== ;Digital downloadiTunes - Music - Dansez (feat.
